  "keyFeatures": [
    "Cross-platform GUI for Unity asset bundle and serialized file editing (Windows, Linux, macOS)",
    "View, edit, import, and export Unity assets of many types (textures, audio, fonts, text, raw data)",
    "Support for both asset bundle files and serialized (assets) files",
    "Bundle decompression and recompression (LZ4, LZMA)",
    "Mod packaging via EMIP (Easy Mod Installer Package) format",
    "Plugin system for extensible asset type support",
    "GameObject hierarchy viewer",
    "Batch export/import for asset bundles via CLI",
    "Addressables support with CRC patch guidance",
    "Dark theme and configurable settings"
  ],
